*ψύχω / psuchō / psoo'-kho
*A primary verb; 
=== Verb ===
to [[breathe]] (voluntarily but gently; thus differing on the one hand from [[πνέω]] {{GG|4154}}, which denotes properly a forcible respiration; and on the other from the base of [[ἀήρ]] {{GG|109}}, which refers properly to an inanimate breeze), that is, (by implication of reduction of temperature by evaporation) to chill (figuratively): wax cold.